ng: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <img title=\"1537185397229065258.jpg\" alt=\"xy2.jpg\" src=\"/static/userImages/20180917/1537185397229065258.jpg\"/> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 谢衣是一个精神力量很强大的人，谢衣的一生，都在为着自己认为理所当然的道路去努力，从没有过半点畏惧和退缩。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;最初的谢衣：<br/></p><p style=\"font: 14px/26.6px Arial,宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">年幼时的谢衣就已经因为不忍目睹流月城内的烈山部诸人苦痛，而立下志愿勤修术法，一心盼望能透过术法为众人解脱痛苦，带来幸福与喜乐，它是个天生的慈悲者。</span></p><p style=\"font: 14px/26.6px Arial,宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;后来在得知大祭司沈夜为了解救族人而与心魔做了恶心的交易之后，谢衣不愿接受牺牲下界的百姓来换取烈山部族人的存续。</span></p><p style=\"font: 14px/26.6px Arial,宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">最终在无数次的劝阻中，谢衣于沈夜的武力比试中落败，在华月与瞳的协助下离开了流月城，朝茫无头绪的下界寻求解救流月城与下界生灵的方法。</span></span></p><p style=\"font: 14px/26.6px Arial,宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">谢衣独自一人在下界游走，学习诸多门派的术法，并进一步完满自己的偃术，踏遍千山万水、读遍经书万卷，只追求一个能够解救流月城与下界生灵的两全之策。</span></span></p><p style=\"font: 14px/26.6px Arial,宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>在下界这22年的时光里，阿阮说谢衣幽默风趣，但在凝视着月亮时，总是不发一语。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　其实，月亮的方向在捐毒往无厌伽蓝靠近后，会清楚的看到月亮旁边那散发着像血一般光辉的流月城。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『余毕生所求，不过穷尽偃术之途，以回护一人一城。』这是谢衣在身死道消之前，留在图谱中的一句话。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『此时相望不相闻，愿逐月华流照君。』</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『我师尊就如同这高天孤月一般，遥不可及、如冰如霜，却又独自照彻漫漫寒夜...』</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　从这几段话不难看出来，谢衣在透过通天之器删减、梳理自己庞大的记忆时，只留存重要事件里头，认为最重要的就是沈夜与流月城。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">当谢衣准备前往捐毒前，似乎早已预料自己的下场，他不但封印了坚持要随行的阿阮于桃园仙居图中，更造了与真人没有两样的偃甲人谢衣来继承自己的偃术与重要的回忆。</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img title=\"1537186564948043523.jpg\" alt=\"xy2.jpg\" src=\"/static/userImages/20180917/1537186564948043523.jpg\"/></span></p><h3 style=\"font: 14px/26.6px Arial,宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font: 18px/26.6px Arial,宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; display: inline !important; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; float: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">偃甲谢衣：</span><span style=\"text-transform: none; line-height: 26.6px; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; word-spacing: 0px; display: inline !important; widows: 1; float: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br/></span></h3><p><span style=\"font: 18px/26.6px Arial,宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; display: inline !important; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; float: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">偃甲谢衣他不是真谢衣，但他也等同于真谢衣，他继承了谢衣的术法、偃术与道，百年的时光让木讷的偃甲与百年前的谢衣性情与理念完全一致，如出一辙。</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font: 18px/26.6px Arial,宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; display: inline !important; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; float: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-size:16px\"> &nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font: 14px/26.6px Arial,宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; display: inline !important; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; float: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> 乐无异一行人一直相处的只不过是偃甲谢衣，但是偃甲谢衣</span></span><span style=\"font: 14px/26.6px Arial,宋体; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; display: inline !important; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; float: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">。但是偃甲谢衣所表现出来的，无异于真的谢衣。</span><br/></span></p><h3 style=\"font: 14px/26.6px Arial,宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; font-size-adjust: none; font-stretch: normal; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><span style=\"font-family:sans-serif\"></span><span style=\"color:#b00000\"></span><span style=\"font-family:sans-serif\"></span><span style=\"color:#007600\"></span><span style=\"font-family:sans-serif\"></span><span style=\"color:#b01100\"></span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 生命至为灿烂，至为珍贵，而又永不重来，身为偃师，万望敬之......畏之.....珍之......重之......<br/></h3><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; <span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">人都是很固执的.....尤其在选择要走的哪条道路时，更是半点也不能强求，所以我也无法告诉你，偃术究竟有何用途.....我只能说，你想要什么，就去做什么，那就是你的道。</span></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 当沈夜在捐毒再次见到谢衣时，他直言当下的心情是『三分意外，七分欣喜』，即便他清楚明白眼前之人不会是真的谢衣，毕竟真的谢衣早在百年前就被他带回流月城，做成了无条件听命行事的傀儡初七。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　而偃甲谢衣的一句『往者已不可追。你我师徒之义早已断绝，昔日种种如川而逝，何必重提。』，瞬间将沈夜愉快的心情、脸上的笑容给击溃。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">忘川是拆解了偃甲人谢衣的头颅、心脏等部位后拼制而成的一把利器，让穿着代表沈夜之道黑衣的初七，手中紧握着代表谢衣之道的偃甲刀，究竟是希望那刀上沾染鲜血，从此堕入无边的黑暗，或是期待百年前的谢衣苏醒，重新带来光明？</span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img title=\"1537187482292044746.jpg\" alt=\"xy3.jpg\" src=\"/static/userImages/20180917/1537187482292044746.jpg\"/></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 初七：</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">沈夜将初七当成条狗、道具、摆设，是把利剑与盾，而初七却把沈夜视为自己生存唯一的意义，是整个世界。</span></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">可为什么全世界的人要的都是谢衣，那初七又算是什么？</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『我不是谢衣。谢衣...早已经不复存在。』初七在说这句话的时候，有忿怒，也有不甘。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">『我并不认为你们能理解...这一百年中，我只注视着一个人，只听从一个人的声音。』</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『他的喜怒就是我的喜怒，他的愿望就是我的愿望。无论发生什么，我不会背弃他第二次。』</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『......你们以为，骄傲如谢衣，会允许自己落入沈夜手中？若是如此，他想要掩盖的那些秘密，岂非一览无余？』</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『......这个胸膛里，早已没有了心跳的声音。』</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『当年，谢衣重伤垂死，被送回流月城，却告回天乏术，最终只得以偃甲和蛊虫续命至今......』</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『所以......你说，一个已经死去的人，会在哪里？』</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　对于初七这个人格来说，谢衣是太灿烂耀眼的存在，承认谢衣的同时就等同于抹煞了生存了百年的自己，</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『意义？』</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『你们活着，有意义吗？微笑哭泣，有意义吗？把我当做谢衣，有意义吗？春秋轮回，枯荣流转，又有什么意义？』</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　真谢衣144年的人生中，当了44年的谢衣，可却当了100年的初七。但最终所有人，连同他视为生命唯一真理的沈夜，也只关注着谢衣，没有人在意他初七的想法与人格。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『在我看来，世间只有一件事，必须不惜代价完成，非要说意义......这就是我唯一的意义。』</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『......我必须将昭明剑心带回流月城......。』</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『否则这一切，永远也无法终结。』</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　而不论是初七还是谢衣，都不愿意背叛沈夜，初七是坚决的为了沈夜而活，而谢衣则是不愿再度背弃师尊，在这一点上面，两个人格的理念是完全一致的。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　这一段话，我觉得不论是谢衣还是初七应该都是相同的，因为唯有昭明剑心能彻底除去心魔，唯有将心魔除去，流月城与下界才能从中获得解脱。这也算是初七与谢衣的共识。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　『若我说是，你们会信？』</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">在神女墓要坍塌的时候，初七斩断了砸向乐无异的巨石，也替内伤不轻的乐无异施法疗伤，耗费庞大法力施展千柱之阵拖住即将坍塌的穹顶。</span></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">初七看到门要关上，而乐无异却执意要跟自己一起离开时，直接以偃甲谢衣改制的长刀忘川，将乐无异击出门外，让他得以生存。</span></p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">『......再见了......这一次，大约真的再也见不到了......』</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　初七不知道是安心还是松懈下来，整个人无力的靠着机关门缓缓坐下，右手压在早已经不再跳动的胸膛，自嘲的说道『呵......谢衣，你真是个......有趣的人哪......』</p><p style=\"font: 14px/26.6px Arial,宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　最终在危急关头，初七决定让继承谢衣偃术与道的无异存活，并贯彻初七决不会背叛沈夜与谢衣不愿背叛师尊第二次的意志，就此长眠与神女墓中。</p><p style=\"font: 14px/26.6px Arial,宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img title=\"1537187779429068064.png\" alt=\"image.png\" src=\"/static/userImages/20180917/1537187779429068064.png\"/></p><p style=\"font: 14px/26.6px Arial,宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;纵观谢衣这一生，当真是没有虚掷一日。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　以自身之能造福无数生灵，以自身之道温暖人心。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　与徒弟是亦师亦友，可惜终究没有多余的时间能留给无异。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　与沈夜是亦子亦友，可惜终究道不同，不相为谋。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　为徒弟，折返黄泉路，只为替他点亮一盏心灯，驱散那无尽的黑暗。</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); font-family: Arial, 宋体; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; line-height: 26.6px; orphans: auto; text-align: start; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\">　　为故人，孤身一人守候在黄泉路上，只为替他撑伞，遮蔽那漫天飞舞的寒雨刺骨。</p><p style=\"font: 14px/26.6px Arial,宋体; margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 15px; color: rgb(43, 43, 43); text-transform: none; text-indent: 0px; letter-spacing: normal; word-spacing: 0px; white-space: normal; widows: 1; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;\"><br/></p>',15,'电视剧  古剑奇谭  谢衣',10),(15,'spring整合redis结合RedisUtil的使用（单机）','redis作为一个高性能的redis数据库，在用作缓存时有非常不错的性能，一般redis都需要与spring来整合使用。对于不经常修改的数据，只做查询使用时，使用redis作缓存能提升查询性能。一.导入maven依赖<dependency>  <groupId>redis.clients</groupId> ','2018-09-18 20:44:35',77,0,'<p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">redis作为一个高性能的redis数据库，在用作缓存时有非常不错的性能，一般redis都需要与spring来整合使用。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\">对于不经常修改的数据，只做查询使用时，使用redis作缓存能提升查询性能。</span><br/></p><p><b><font size=\"5\">一.导入maven依赖</font></b></p><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">&lt;dependency&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;redis.clients&lt;/groupId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;jedis&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;version&gt;2.6.0&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n\n&lt;dependency&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.data&lt;/groupId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;spring-data-redis&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;version&gt;1.4.2.RELEASE&lt;/version&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;</pre><p><b><font size=\"5\">二.配置相关配置文件<br/><br/></font></b></p><p><b>&nbsp;1.配置redis.properties</b></p><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">#ip地址\nredis.hostName=182.61.52.221\n#端口号\nredis.port=6379\n#如果有密码\nredis.password=123456\n#客户端超时时间单位是毫秒&nbsp;默认是2000\nredis.timeout=10000&nbsp;&nbsp;\n\n#最大空闲数\nredis.maxIdle=300&nbsp;&nbsp;\n#连接池的最大数据库连接数。设为0表示无限制,如果是jedis&nbsp;2.4以后用redis.maxTotal\n#redis.maxActive=600\n#控制一个pool可分配多少个jedis实例,用来替换上面的redis.maxActive,如果是jedis&nbsp;2.4以后用该属性\nredis.maxTotal=1000&nbsp;&nbsp;\n#最大建立连接等待时间。如果超过此时间将接到异常。设为-1表示无限制。\nredis.maxWaitMillis=1000&nbsp;&nbsp;\n#连接的最小空闲时间&nbsp;默认1800000毫秒(30分钟)\nredis.minEvictableIdleTimeMillis=300000&nbsp;&nbsp;\n#每次释放连接的最大数目,默认3\nredis.numTestsPerEvictionRun=1024&nbsp;&nbsp;\n#逐出扫描的时间间隔(毫秒)&nbsp;如果为负数,则不运行逐出线程,&nbsp;默认-1\nredis.timeBetweenEvictionRunsMillis=30000&nbsp;&nbsp;\n#是否在从池中取出连接前进行检验,如果检验失败,则从池中去除连接并尝试取出另一个\nredis.testOnBorrow=true\n#在空闲时检查有效性,&nbsp;默认false\nredis.testWhileIdle=true</pre><p><b><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\"></span>&nbsp;2.spring相关配置。</b></p><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">&lt;!--&nbsp;加载配置文件&nbsp;--&gt;\n&lt;context:property-placeholder&nbsp;location=&quot;classpath:redis.pro\nperties&quot;&nbsp;ignore-unresolvable=&quot;true&quot;/&gt;\n&lt;!--&nbsp;redis连接池配置--&gt;\n&lt;bean&nbsp;id=&quot;jedisPoolConfig&quot;&nbsp;class=&quot;redis.clients.jedis.JedisPoolConfig&quot;&nbsp;&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;!--最大空闲数--&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;maxIdle&quot;&nbsp;value=&quot;${redis.maxIdle}&quot;&nbsp;/&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;!--连接池的最大数据库连接数&nbsp;&nbsp;--&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;maxTotal&quot;&nbsp;value=&quot;${redis.maxTotal}&quot;&nbsp;/&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;!--最大建立连接等待时间--&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;maxWaitMillis&quot;&nbsp;value=&quot;${redis.maxWaitMillis}&quot;&nbsp;/&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;!--逐出连接的最小空闲时间&nbsp;默认1800000毫秒(30分钟)--&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;minEvictableIdleTimeMillis&quot;&nbsp;value=&quot;${redis.minEvictableIdleTimeMillis}&quot;&nbsp;/&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;!--每次逐出检查时&nbsp;逐出的最大数目&nbsp;如果为负数就是&nbsp;:&nbsp;1/abs(n),&nbsp;默认3--&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;numTestsPerEvictionRun&quot;&nbsp;value=&quot;${redis.numTestsPerEvictionRun}&quot;&nbsp;/&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;!--逐出扫描的时间间隔(毫秒)&nbsp;如果为负数,则不运行逐出线程,&nbsp;默认-1--&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;timeBetweenEvictionRunsMillis&quot;&nbsp;value=&quot;${redis.timeBetweenEvictionRunsMillis}&quot;&nbsp;/&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;!--是否在从池中取出连接前进行检验,如果检验失败,则从池中去除连接并尝试取出另一个--&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;testOnBorrow&quot;&nbsp;value=&quot;${redis.testOnBorrow}&quot;&nbsp;/&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;!--在空闲时检查有效性,&nbsp;默认false&nbsp;&nbsp;--&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;testWhileIdle&quot;&nbsp;value=&quot;${redis.testWhileIdle}&quot;&nbsp;/&gt;\n&lt;/bean&nbsp;&gt;\n\n&lt;!--redis连接工厂&nbsp;--&gt;\n&lt;bean&nbsp;id=&quot;jedisConnectionFactory&quot;&nbsp;class=&quot;org.springframework.data.redis.connection.jedis.JedisConnectionFactory&quot;&nbsp;destroy-method=&quot;destroy&quot;&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;poolConfig&quot;&nbsp;ref=&quot;jedisPoolConfig&quot;&gt;&lt;/property&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;!--IP地址&nbsp;--&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;hostName&quot;&nbsp;value=&quot;${redis.hostName}&quot;&gt;&lt;/property&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;!--端口号&nbsp;&nbsp;--&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;port&quot;&nbsp;value=&quot;${redis.port}&quot;&gt;&lt;/property&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;!--如果Redis设置有密码,没有的话就注释掉下面的配置&nbsp;&nbsp;--&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;password&quot;&nbsp;value=&quot;${redis.password}&quot;&nbsp;/&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;!--客户端超时时间单位是毫秒&nbsp;&nbsp;--&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;timeout&quot;&nbsp;value=&quot;${redis.timeout}&quot;&gt;&lt;/property&gt;\n&lt;/bean&gt;\n\n&lt;!--redis操作模版,使用该对象可以操作redis&nbsp;&nbsp;--&gt;\n&lt;bean&nbsp;id=&quot;redisTemplate&quot;&nbsp;class=&quot;org.springframework.data.redis.core.RedisTemplate&quot;&nbsp;&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;connectionFactory&quot;&nbsp;ref=&quot;jedisConnectionFactory&quot;&nbsp;/&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;!--如果不配置Serializer，那么存储的时候缺省使用String，如果用User类型存储，那么会提示错误User&nbsp;can&#39;t&nbsp;cast&nbsp;to&nbsp;String！！&nbsp;&nbsp;--&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;keySerializer&quot;&nbsp;&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;bean&nbsp;class=&quot;org.springframework.data.redis.serializer.StringRedisSerializer&quot;&nbsp;/&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/property&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;valueSerializer&quot;&nbsp;&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;bean&nbsp;class=&quot;org.springframework.data.redis.serializer.JdkSerializationRedisSerializer&quot;&nbsp;/&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;/property&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;!--开启事务&nbsp;&nbsp;--&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;property&nbsp;name=&quot;enableTransactionSupport&quot;&nbsp;value=&quot;true&quot;&gt;&lt;/property&gt;\n&lt;/bean&nbsp;&gt;</pre><p><br/></p><p>3.RedisUtil</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">@Component\npublic&nbsp;final&nbsp;class&nbsp;RedisUtil&nbsp;{\n\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@Resource\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;private&nbsp;RedisTemplate&lt;Serializable,&nbsp;Object&gt;&nbsp;redisTemplate;\n\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/**\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;写入缓存\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;@param&nbsp;key\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;@param&nbsp;value\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;@return\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*/\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;boolean&nbsp;set(final&nbsp;String&nbsp;key,&nbsp;Object&nbsp;value)&nbsp;{\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;boolean&nbsp;result&nbsp;=&nbsp;false;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;try&nbsp;{\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ValueOperations&lt;Serializable,&nbsp;Object&gt;&nbsp;operations&nbsp;=&nbsp;redisTemplate.opsForValue();\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;operations.set(key,&nbsp;value);\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;result&nbsp;=&nbsp;true;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;catch&nbsp;(Exception&nbsp;e)&nbsp;{\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;e.printStackTrace();\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;result;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\n\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;/**\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;读取缓存\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;@param&nbsp;key\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*&nbsp;@return\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;*/\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;Object&nbsp;get(final&nbsp;String&nbsp;key)&nbsp;{\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;Object&nbsp;result&nbsp;=&nbsp;null;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;ValueOperations&lt;Serializable,&nbsp;Object&gt;&nbsp;operations&nbsp;=&nbsp;redisTemplate.opsForValue();\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;result&nbsp;=&nbsp;operations.get(key);\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;result;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</pre><p>至此，即可通过redisUtil去操作了。<br/></p>',14,'spring redis',0),(17,'java8新特性','一.lambda表达式    Lambda 表达式，也可称为闭包，它是推动 Java 8 发布的最重要新特性。     Lambda 允许把函数作为一个方法的参数（函数作为参数传递进方法中）。     使用 Lambda 表达式可以使代码变的更加简洁紧凑。     语法格式：(parameters) -> e','2018-09-19 14:45:45',41,0,'<h3>一.lambda表达式<br/></h3><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 13px;\">Lambda 表达式，也可称为闭包，它是推动 Java 8 发布的最重要新特性。</span></p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;Lambda 允许把函数作为一个方法的参数（函数作为参数传递进方法中）。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;使用 Lambda 表达式可以使代码变的更加简洁紧凑。</p><p style=\"border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">&nbsp; 语法格式：</span><br/></p><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">(parameters)&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;expression\n或(parameters)&nbsp;-&gt;{&nbsp;statements;&nbsp;}</pre><p style=\"border: 0px; margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; line-height: 2em; word-wrap: break-word; word-break: break-all; font-size: 13px; font-family: &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, Helvetica, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;Noto Sans CJK SC&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp; lambda表达式的简单例子：<br/></p><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">//&nbsp;1.&nbsp;不需要参数,返回值为&nbsp;5&nbsp;\n&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;()&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;5&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;2.&nbsp;接收一个参数(数字类型),返回其2倍的值\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;x&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;2&nbsp;*&nbsp;x&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\n//&nbsp;3.&nbsp;接受2个参数(数字),并返回他们的差值&nbsp;&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(x,&nbsp;y)&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;x&nbsp;–&nbsp;y&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\n//&nbsp;4.&nbsp;接收2个int型整数,返回他们的和&nbsp;&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(int&nbsp;x,&nbsp;int&nbsp;y)&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;x&nbsp;+&nbsp;y&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;\n//&nbsp;5.&nbsp;接受一个&nbsp;string&nbsp;对象,并在控制台打印,不返回任何值(看起来像是返回void)&nbsp;&nbsp;\n\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(String&nbsp;s)&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;System.out.print(s)</pre><p><br/></p><p>lambda实现runnable接口</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<br/></p><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">//&nbsp;1.1使用匿名内部类&nbsp;&nbsp;new&nbsp;Thread(new&nbsp;Runnable()&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@Override&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;void&nbsp;run()&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;System.out.println(&quot;Hello&nbsp;world&nbsp;!&quot;);&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;}).start();&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;1.2使用&nbsp;lambda&nbsp;expression&nbsp;&nbsp;new&nbsp;Thread(()&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;System.out.println(&quot;Hello&nbsp;world&nbsp;!&quot;)).start();&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;2.1使用匿名内部类&nbsp;&nbsp;Runnable&nbsp;race1&nbsp;=&nbsp;new&nbsp;Runnable()&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@Override&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;void&nbsp;run()&nbsp;{&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;System.out.println(&quot;Hello&nbsp;world&nbsp;!&quot;);&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}&nbsp;&nbsp;};&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;2.2使用&nbsp;lambda&nbsp;expression&nbsp;&nbsp;Runnable&nbsp;race2&nbsp;=&nbsp;()&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;System.out.println(&quot;Hello&nbsp;world&nbsp;!&quot;);</pre><p><br/></p><p>使用lambda排序</p><p><br/></p><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">//&nbsp;3.2&nbsp;使用&nbsp;lambda&nbsp;expression&nbsp;排序,根据最后一个字母&nbsp;&nbsp;Comparator&lt;String&gt;&nbsp;sortByLastLetter&nbsp;=&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(String&nbsp;s1,&nbsp;String&nbsp;s2)&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;(s1.charAt(s1.length()&nbsp;-&nbsp;1)&nbsp;-&nbsp;s2.charAt(s2.length()&nbsp;-&nbsp;1));&nbsp;&nbsp;Arrays.sort(players,&nbsp;sortByLastLetter);&nbsp;&nbsp;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;//&nbsp;3.3&nbsp;or&nbsp;this&nbsp;&nbsp;Arrays.sort(players,&nbsp;(String&nbsp;s1,&nbsp;String&nbsp;s2)&nbsp;-&gt;&nbsp;(s1.charAt(s1.length()&nbsp;-&nbsp;1)&nbsp;-&nbsp;s2.charAt(s2.length()&nbsp;-&nbsp;1)));</pre><p><br/></p>',16,'java8 新特性',0),(18,'springboot入门介绍及HelloWorld实现','一.什么是springBoot        Spring Boot是由Pivotal团队提供的全新框架，其设计目的是用来简化新Spring应用的初始搭建以及开发过程。该框架使用了特定的方式来进行配置（约定大于配置的原则），从而使开发人员不再需要定义样板化的配置。用我的话来理解，就是spring boot其实','2018-09-19 22:17:53',13,0,'<h2>一.什么是springBoot<br/></h2><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544000029563904px; line-height: 27.2000007629395px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Spring Boot是由Pivotal团队提供的全新框架，其设计目的是用来简化新Spring应用的初始搭建以及开发过程。该框架使用了特定的方式来进行配置（约定大于配置的原则），从而使开发人员不再需要定义样板化的配置。用我的话来理解，就是spring boot其实不是什么新的框架，它默认配置了很多框架的使用方式，就像maven整合了所有的jar包，spring boot整合了所有的框架（不知道这样比喻是否合适）。</span></p><h2>二.使用springboot的优点<br/></h2><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; 平时如果我们需要搭建一个spring web项目的时候需要怎么做呢？</p><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin: 1.2em 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544000029563904px; line-height: 27.2000007629395px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\">1）配置web.xml，加载spring和spring mvc</p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\">2）配置数据库连接、配置spring事务</p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\">3）配置加载配置文件的读取，开启注解</p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\">4）配置日志文件</p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\">…</p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\">配置完成之后部署tomcat 调试</p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\">…</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 112, 192);\">而使用springboot：</span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">快速创建独立运行的Spring项目以及与主流框架集成 </span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">使用嵌入式的Servlet容器，应用无需打成WAR包</span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">starters自动依赖与版本控制 – 大量的自动配置，简化开发，也可修改默认值</span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> 无需配置XML，无代码生成，开箱即用&nbsp;</span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"> 准生产环境的运行时应用监控 – 与云计算的天然集成</span></p><h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"></h2></li></ul><h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; clear: both; word-wrap: break-word !important; min-height: 1em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important;\"><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">三.HelloWorld实现</span><br/></h2><p><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; 使用idea创建工程，选择spring initializr，默认就是Springboot项目地址。</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<img title=\"1537365312949010847.png\" alt=\"image.png\" src=\"/static/userImages/20180919/1537365312949010847.png\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\">选择初始化数据，</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><img title=\"1537365381224061146.png\" alt=\"image.png\" src=\"/static/userImages/20180919/1537365381224061146.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\">这里包含很多的spring集成依赖，入门只用选择web依赖</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><img title=\"1537365438528098998.png\" alt=\"image.png\" src=\"/static/userImages/20180919/1537365438528098998.png\"/></p><p>完成以后，idea会自动帮我们构建项目。</p><p><br/></p><p>首先看pom.xml</p><p><br/></p><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">&lt;parent&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-parent&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;version&gt;2.0.5.RELEASE&lt;/version&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;relativePath/&gt;&nbsp;&lt;!--&nbsp;lookup&nbsp;parent&nbsp;from&nbsp;repository&nbsp;--&gt;\n&lt;/parent&gt;</pre><p>spring集成自一个核心父级依赖，包含一些必须参数配置。</p><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">&lt;dependency&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-web&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;</pre><p>这个是springboot的web依赖。</p><p><br/></p><p>springboot的推荐工程结构。</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">com\n&nbsp;&nbsp;+-&nbsp;example\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;+-&nbsp;myproject\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;+-&nbsp;Application.java\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;+-&nbsp;domain\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;+-&nbsp;Customer.java\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;+-&nbsp;CustomerRepository.java\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;+-&nbsp;service\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;+-&nbsp;CustomerService.java\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;+-&nbsp;controller\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|&nbsp;&nbsp;+-&nbsp;CustomerController.java\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;|</pre><p><br/></p><ul class=\" list-paddingleft-2\" style=\"margin: 1.2em 0px; padding: 0px 0px 0px 2em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, &#39;Helvetica Neue&#39;, &#39;PingFang SC&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei UI&#39;, &#39;Microsoft YaHei&#39;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 17px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: 0.544000029563904px; line-height: 27.2000007629395px; orphans: auto; text-align: justify; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: 1; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\">1<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">、Application.java 建议放到跟目录下面,主要用于做一些框架配置</span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\">2<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">、domain目录主要用于实体（Entity）与数据访问层</span><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">（Repository）</span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">3、service 层主要是业务类代码</span></p></li><li><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\">4、<span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">controller 负责页面访问控制</span></p></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\">编写一个Controller</p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; clear: both; min-height: 1em;\"><br/></p><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">package&nbsp;com.example.demo.Controller;\n\nimport&nbsp;org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.RequestMapping;\nimport&nbsp;org.springframework.web.bind.annotation.RestController;\n\n@RestController\npublic&nbsp;class&nbsp;HelloController&nbsp;{\n\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;@RequestMapping(&quot;hello&quot;)\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;String&nbsp;hello(){\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;return&nbsp;&quot;hello&quot;;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\n}</pre><p><br/></p><p>直接启动<span style=\"display: inline !important; float: none; background-color: transparent; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font,BlinkMacSystemFont,&quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;,&quot;PingFang SC&quot;,&quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;,&quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;,Arial,sans-serif; font-size: 16px; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: 0.54px; orphans: 2; text-align: justify; text-decoration: none; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; word-spacing: 0px;\">Application.java</span></p><p><br/></p><p><img title=\"1537366550541017911.png\" alt=\"image.png\" src=\"/static/userImages/20180919/1537366550541017911.png\"/></p><p>可见内嵌的Tomcat启动成功。</p><p><br/></p><p>输入localhost:8080/hello</p><p><br/></p><p>。<img title=\"1537366613408075245.png\" alt=\"image.png\" src=\"/static/userImages/20180919/1537366613408075245.png\"/></p><p>可见返回了json数据。</p>',17,'springboot',0),(19,'springboot helloworld探究','一.pom文件<parent>    <groupId>org.springframework.boot</groupId>    <artifactId>spring-boot-starter-parent</artifactId>    <version>2.0.5.RELEASE</version>  ','2018-09-19 23:06:59',31,0,'<h2>一.pom文件<br/></h2><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">&lt;parent&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-parent&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;version&gt;2.0.5.RELEASE&lt;/version&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;relativePath/&gt;&nbsp;&lt;!--&nbsp;lookup&nbsp;parent&nbsp;from&nbsp;repository&nbsp;--&gt;\n&lt;/parent&gt;\n它的父项目\n&lt;parent&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-dependencies&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;version&gt;2.0.5.RELEASE&lt;/version&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;relativePath&gt;../../spring-boot-dependencies&lt;/relativePath&gt;\n&lt;/parent&gt;\n它来管理spring的所有版本依赖。</pre><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\">springboot将所有与spring集成的依赖统一管理起来。</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\">以后我们导入依赖默认是不需要写版本</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\"><br/></span></p><h2>二.启动器<br/></h2><p><br/></p><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">&lt;dependency&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-web&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n按住ctr点进去，实际依赖如下:\n&lt;dependency&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;version&gt;2.0.5.RELEASE&lt;/version&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;scope&gt;compile&lt;/scope&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n&lt;dependency&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-json&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;version&gt;2.0.5.RELEASE&lt;/version&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;scope&gt;compile&lt;/scope&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n&lt;dependency&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-tomcat&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;version&gt;2.0.5.RELEASE&lt;/version&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;scope&gt;compile&lt;/scope&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n&lt;dependency&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;org.hibernate.validator&lt;/groupId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;hibernate-validator&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;version&gt;6.0.12.Final&lt;/version&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;scope&gt;compile&lt;/scope&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n&lt;dependency&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework&lt;/groupId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;spring-web&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;version&gt;5.0.9.RELEASE&lt;/version&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;scope&gt;compile&lt;/scope&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;\n&lt;dependency&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework&lt;/groupId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;spring-webmvc&lt;/artifactId&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;version&gt;5.0.9.RELEASE&lt;/version&gt;\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&lt;scope&gt;compile&lt;/scope&gt;\n&lt;/dependency&gt;</pre><p><span style=\"color:#000124\">spring-boot-starter-web：<br/>&nbsp; spring-boot-starter：spring-boot场景启动器；帮我们导入了web模块正常运行所依赖的组件；<br/>&nbsp; <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\">Spring Boot将所有的功能场景都抽取出来，做成一个个的starters（启动器），只需要在项目里面引入这些starter 相关场景的所有依赖都会导入进来。要用什么功能就导入什么场景的启动器</span></span></p><p><br/></p><h2>三.主程序入口类<br/></h2><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">@SpringBootApplication\npublic&nbsp;class&nbsp;DemoApplication&nbsp;{\n\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;public&nbsp;static&nbsp;void&nbsp;main(String[]&nbsp;args)&nbsp;{\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;SpringApplication.run(DemoApplication.class,&nbsp;args);\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}\n}</pre><p>&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">@SpringBootApplication:</span>&nbsp;</p><p>Spring Boot应用标注在某个类上说明这个类是SpringBoot的主配置类，SpringBoot 就应该运行这个类的main方法来启动SpringBoot应用；</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">@SpringBootConﬁguration:</span></p><p>Spring Boot的配置类；<br/>&nbsp; 标注在某个类上，表示这是一个Spring Boot的配置类；</p><p><br/></p><p>这个注解包含的注解:</p><pre class=\"brush:java;toolbar:false\">@Target({ElementType.TYPE})\n@Retention(RetentionPolicy.RUNTIME)\n@Documented\n@Inherited\n@SpringBootConfiguration\n@EnableAutoConfiguration\n@ComponentScan(\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;excludeFilters&nbsp;=&nbsp;{@Filter(\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;type&nbsp;=&nbsp;FilterType.CUSTOM,\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;classes&nbsp;=&nbsp;{TypeExcludeFilter.class}\n),&nbsp;@Filter(\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;type&nbsp;=&nbsp;FilterType.CUSTOM,\n&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;classes&nbsp;=&nbsp;{AutoConfigurationExcludeFilter.class}\n)}\n)</pre><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">@EnableAutoConﬁguration：</span></p><p>开启自动配置功能；<br/>&nbsp; 以前我们需要配置的东西，Spring Boot帮我们自动配置；@EnableAutoConﬁguration告诉SpringBoot开启自 动配置功能；这样自动配置才能生效；&nbsp;</p><p><br/></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 80);\">@AutoConﬁgurationPackage：</span></p><p>自动配置包<br/>&nbsp; @Import(AutoConﬁgurationPackages.Registrar.class)：<br/>&nbsp; Spring的底层注解@Import，给容器中导入一个组件；导入的组件由 AutoConﬁgurationPackages.Registrar.class；</p><p><br/></p><p>springboot集成了很多的注解，这些核心注解底层帮我们自动生成导入很多以前的需要自己配置的东西。<br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p>',17,'springboot',0),(20,'从零开始搭建xwiki','最近公司需要搭建一个能把常规工作进行文档整理平台，无论是平时工作处理或是工作交接，实时的维护文档资料可以提高工作效率。搜查一阵对比之后，觉得xwiki综合来说比较好，而且作为Java开发人员，肯定首选java做的东西啦，因此，搭建xwiki的工作就此展开啦。搭建准备工作（本人是在centos7下）      ','2018-09-21 15:29:20',16,0,'<p>最近公司需要搭建一个能把<span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">常规工作进行文档整理平台，<span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">无论是平时工作处理或是工作交接，实时的维护文档资料可以提高工作效率。</span>搜查一阵对比之后，觉得xwiki综合来说比较好，而且作为Java开发人员，肯定首选java做的东西啦，因此，搭建xwiki的工作就此展开啦。</span></p><p><br/></p><p><img src=\"/static/userImages/20180921/1537527852440042148.jpg\" title=\"1537527852440042148.jpg\" alt=\"QQ图片20180921190258.jpg\"/></p><h3 style=\"text-align: justify;\">搭建准备工作（本人是在centos7下）<br/></h3><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;<br/></p><h4>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.安装jdk&nbsp; 教程：<a href=\"http://182.61.52.221/blog/articles/4.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://182.61.52.221/blog/articles/4.html</a></h4><h4>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2.安装tomcat&nbsp; 教程：<a href=\"http://182.61.52.221/blog/articles/5.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://182.61.52.221/blog/articles/5.html</a></h4><h4>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.安装mysql&nbsp; 教程：<a href=\"http://182.61.52.221/blog/articles/8.html\" target=\"_blank\">http://182.61.52.221/blog/articles/8.html</a>&nbsp; &nbsp;（本人实际装的是mysql5.7,其它的可能不适配，建议装5.7及以下版本）</h4><p><br/></p><h3>安装配置office s