ackground-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">进入</span></span>： cd&nbsp;&nbsp;/opt/zh-CN/RPMS&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">安装所有的rpm</span>：yum -y&nbsp;localinstall&nbsp; *.rpm</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">接着，我们进入这个目录</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;#cd /opt/zh-CN/RPMS/desktop-integration，</span></span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all;\">#ls，</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify;\">会看见四个rpm文件，我们要安装openoffice4.1.2-redhat-menus-4.1.2-9782.noarch.rpm</span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">直接安装openoffice4.1.2-redhat-menus-4.1.2-9782.noarch.rpm会报错，</span></span></p><p><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;所以使用</span><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">#<span style=\"font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\">rpm -ivh --force&nbsp; openoffice4.1.2-redhat-menus-4.1.2-9782.noarch.rpm</span></span><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">,进行强制安装</span></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">openOffice己经安装完成，默认会安装在/opt下.</span></span></p><h4><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-align: justify; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;2.启动<br/></span></h4><p><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); text-align: justify; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;\">1.进入opt(默认安装路径)下openofiice4的program目录：&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</span><span style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\">cd&nbsp;/opt/openoffice4/program</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　2.执行: soffice -headless -accept=&quot;socket,host=127.0.0.1,port=8100;urp;&quot; -nofirststartwizard &amp;&nbsp;</span></p><ul style=\"margin-left: 30px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">验证成功:</span></p></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">　1.netstat -lnp |grep 8100&nbsp; 出现 &quot;tcp&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 0&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 0 127.0.0.1:8100&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 0.0.0.0:*&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;LISTEN&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 13841/soffice.bin&nbsp;&quot;.</span></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 0);\">报错处理:</span><br/></p><ul style=\"margin-left: 30px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><br/></p></li><li><p>&quot;/opt/openoffice4/program/soffice.bin: error while loading shared libraries: libXext.so.6: cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory&quot;</p></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　　处理:&nbsp;安装<span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\">libXext.so.6:yum install libXext.x86_64</span>.</p><ul style=\"margin-left: 30px; padding: 0px; word-break: break-all; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\" class=\" list-paddingleft-2\"><li><p><br/></p></li><li><p>&quot;no suitable windowing system found, exiting.&quot;</p></li></ul><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">　　处理:&nbsp;安装桌面环境: <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 176, 240);\">yum groupinstall &quot;X Window System&quot;</span>.</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">至此，openoffice的安装工作完成。</p><p style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><br/></p><h3 style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; font-family: Verdana, Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;安装xwiki并配置一些配置</span><br/></h3><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.上传war包<br/></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">#cd /usr/local/tomcat/webapps</span><span style=\"color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">,然后建立一个xwiki的文件夹，</span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: arial, helvetica, sans-serif; font-size: 18px;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box; outline: 0px; word-break: break-all; color: rgb(79, 79, 79); font-family: -apple-system, &quot;SF UI Text&quot;, Arial, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, &quot;WenQuanYi Micro Hei&quot;, sans-serif, SimHei, SimSun; text-align: justify; background-color: rgb(2